Oscar GC
========

Oscar GC is a custom distribution of Goose, an open-source agent platform.
See LICENSE for license terms (Apache License, Version 2.0).

This product includes software developed by the following projects:

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Goose
Copyright 2024 Block, Inc.
Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
https://github.com/aaif-goose/goose (formerly https://github.com/block/goose)

Oscar GC forks Goose as a custom distribution under upstream's
CUSTOM_DISTROS.md. The Rust agent core remains substantially upstream;
the desktop UI (`ui/desktop/src/`) and sibling MCP servers
(`oscar-onboarding-mcp`, `oscar-memory-mcp`) are Oscar GC additions.

