  Upstream commit: 7c2efe61524b14c632bee8f14d9bbcbdd85d0cfd
  Upstream date:   2026-05-20
  Pull date:       2026-05-20

The Oscar GC adaptation (`RUBRIC.adapted.md` + the runner under
